g.text: Okay, I admit that calling your interest in me a "manic pixie dream girl act" was inconsiderate.

g.title: j1634300487
g.text: ya! just like a storybook. gotta leave ur peaceful little village and slay a big dragon so u can truly appreciate the peace, y'know?

g.title: j1521885532
g.text: Well, it was. You're cute. I mean unbelievably cute. I just find it hard to believe.

g.title: j1713270264
g.text: You caught that, huh?

g.title: j3567636979
g.text: Nobody's actually bubbly and fun all the time.

g.title: j726107971
g.text: I can see a deeper side to you, Aoi. You're tough. You're more than pop songs and emoticons.

g.title: j1966767238
g.text: Haha I don't know much about dragons, but I know a lot about Orowyrms.

g.title: j218014631

g.text: how am I supposed to receive that?

g.title: j244707838
g.text: nobody's serious and boring all the time either

g.title: j4225254502
g.text: it concerns me that u don't think depth, toughness, pop songs, and emoticons can go together

g.title: j204097887
g.text: Oro-whats? :O

g.title: j719195382
g.text: Listen, I think you're amazing. I said that manic pixie crap because I doubt myself, not you. I'm sorry.

g.title: j4203585606

g.title: j3254470507

g.text: I get that u have bad days. who doesn't, right?

g.title: j268542085
